Fuck off, both of ya.

48:29.000 --> 48:31.120
He tells Linda everything.

48:32.360 --> 48:33.640
Every single thing.

48:33.720 --> 48:36.160
Yeah, well, we'll see...

48:42.200 --> 48:44.800
We're going to miss you when
you're gone now, Arthur.

48:47.680 --> 48:49.760
Just drive the fucking car.

49:09.080 --> 49:10.080
(SIGHING)

49:19.480 --> 49:22.640
Private Let so reporting
for duty, Sergeant Major.

49:23.760 --> 49:25.360
At ease, Private.

49:28.520 --> 49:29.920
Good to see you.

49:33.680 --> 49:36.360
ARTHUR: Seven left. Out of 50.

49:37.120 --> 49:38.960
Should I get them tea?

49:39.040 --> 49:40.160
Get 'em beer.

49:40.240 --> 49:42.800
They used to run on it
like cars on petrol.

49:42.880 --> 49:44.720
Give them the black country stuff.

49:44.800 --> 49:47.000
It's in the barrel with the tack.

49:47.680 --> 49:49.760
They're going to fucking clean me out.

49:50.200 --> 49:52.360
ARTHUR: Whatever they take,
they'll put back.

49:52.600 --> 49:53.640
Good men.

49:53.720 --> 49:55.160
John, Arthur.

49:55.680 --> 49:57.240
You remember these boys.

49:59.320 --> 50:02.600
Well, if it ain't the Tipton
Fucking Clay Kickers, eh?

50:03.160 --> 50:05.320
-Clay Kickers.
-Come here, you.

50:06.440 --> 50:08.400
-How are ya? Good to see ya.
-How are ya?

50:09.680 --> 50:11.320
-Nice.
-Good to see ya.

50:12.160 --> 50:13.520
And this is William Let so.

50:13.600 --> 50:15.760
From the South African
Native Labour Corps.

50:15.840 --> 50:19.000
Sent to Flanders from the
Bloemfontein diamond mines.

50:19.560 --> 50:22.120
And the best tunneller I ever met.

50:22.200 --> 50:24.400
So, there's three cellars
underneath the house.

50:24.480 --> 50:26.480
Wine, kitchen and septic.

50:26.600 --> 50:28.520
There's a tunnel here that runs

50:28.600 --> 50:32.080
from the house underneath the river
to an underground strong room.

50:32.160 --> 50:34.720
Now, this used to be
the palace treasury.

50:34.800 --> 50:36.800
The tunnel runs directly west

50:36.880 --> 50:39.760
and it's separated from
the house by three iron doors

50:39.840 --> 50:41.680
with locks we can't open.

50:42.000 --> 50:46.800
We need our tunnel to run from here
and hit the strong room, direct.

50:50.720 --> 50:52.600
(FOOTSTEPS APPROACHING)

50:55.400 --> 50:57.120
(KEYS JINGLING)

51:27.120 --> 51:29.480
Primrose Hill 23. Ada Thorne.

51:32.040 --> 51:33.120
Ada?

51:33.640 --> 51:35.560
Is Michael still there?

51:39.200 --> 51:41.960
Right, would you tell him
that I have taken the car?

51:42.040 --> 51:43.880
He can take the train.

51:44.760 --> 51:47.800
And try and find out why
he's been so bloody sour lately.

52:15.240 --> 52:16.680
(DOOR OPENING)

52:17.640 --> 52:18.960
(CLOSES DRAWER)

53:01.000 --> 53:02.280
(TOMMY CLEARS THROAT)

53:09.480 --> 53:10.480
(SIGHS)

53:24.760 --> 53:25.760
(EXHALING)

53:29.040 --> 53:32.360
You shouldn't go looking through
other people's private things.

53:32.440 --> 53:33.840
He's my son.

53:35.440 --> 53:38.080
The bullet was mine.
I never got a chance to fire it.

53:38.160 --> 53:41.640
And the gypsy rules
say it must be passed on...

53:41.720 --> 53:43.160
It's not about rules, Pol.

53:43.240 --> 53:44.560
It's about he asked me.

53:47.040 --> 53:48.680
It's about he told me

53:48.760 --> 53:50.280
why he wanted to do it.

53:51.280 --> 53:52.720
Now, if I tell you,

53:53.640 --> 53:55.520
I can't take the knowledge back.

53:58.040 --> 53:59.440
Better off without it.

54:04.280 --> 54:05.800
So this is when
he was with the parish...

54:05.920 --> 54:07.120
Better off without it, Pol.

54:19.560 --> 54:22.240
This is when he was with the Fathers.

54:22.600 --> 54:25.960
This is when he was in
the care of the Holy Fathers.

54:26.680 --> 54:28.760
Michael wants it
so you don't know...

54:39.400 --> 54:41.240
-That priest...
-That priest

54:42.760 --> 54:45.720
who was there when he was taken in.

54:46.960 --> 54:49.400
And who is still walking
the fucking Earth.

54:49.480 --> 54:50.680
Fuck...

54:59.160 --> 55:00.200
Fuck...

55:00.280 --> 55:01.960
He asked me, Pol...

55:02.320 --> 55:04.000
And I said yes.

55:08.640 --> 55:10.040
And I said,

55:10.440 --> 55:14.680
"You put a bullet
in that fucker's brains.

55:16.680 --> 55:18.960
"By order of the Peaky Blinders."

55:24.520 --> 55:25.520
(SNIFFS)

55:26.640 --> 55:27.960
(EXHALING)

55:31.240 --> 55:32.280
No.

55:34.600 --> 55:35.800
Not my son.

55:39.320 --> 55:40.960
He'll still be as
dead if Arthur does it.

55:41.320 --> 55:43.440
And part of him will always stay dead.

55:47.320 --> 55:49.640
-I swear to God...
-In whose house it took place...

55:49.720 --> 55:52.160
If my son pulls the trigger,

55:53.600 --> 55:57.840
I will bring this whole fucking
organisation down around your ears.

56:10.520 --> 56:12.520
(THEME SONG PLAYING)

56:12.544 --> 56:17.544
http://hiqve.com/
